verbose_text: To assess whether the glucose intolerance of Fh1betaKO mice is mediated by HIF1alpha stabilization, we crossed Fh1betaKO and Hif1alpha fl/fl mice to produce beta cell specific deletion of both Fh1 and Hif1alpha (Fh1Hif1alphabetaKO mice).
evidence: glucose intolerance of Fh1betaKO mice is mediated by HIF1alpha
